msgctxt "3866"
msgid "中岡だ。……入るぞ。"
msgstr "It's Nakaoka. ...... I'll enter."

msgctxt "3896"
msgid "岡田以蔵、お前が捕まえたってな。"
msgstr "Okada Izo, you got caught."

msgctxt "3934"
msgid ""
"皮肉なもんだ。\n"
"かつての仲間をその手で捕まえて、\n"
"それが武市の危機にも繋がっちまうとはな。"
msgstr ""
"It's ironic. I don't think it would lead to the crisis in Takeshi by "
"catching the former friends with their hands."

msgctxt "4030"
msgid ""
"そう落ち込むな。\n"
"あの武市はそう簡単に終わる男じゃねえ。"
msgstr ""
"Don't be so depressed. That Takeichi is not a man who finishes so easily."

msgctxt "4087"
msgid ""
"あいつなら容堂公に呼び戻された理由も\n"
"わかっているはずだ。\n"
"きっとあいつなりに手を打ってある。"
msgstr ""
"He must know why he was called back to Toyoshige. I'm sure he's doing "
"something about it."

msgctxt "4182"
msgid "だといいがな。"
msgstr "I hope it is."

msgctxt "4197"
msgid "心配か？　武市のこと。"
msgstr "Are you worried? Takeshi."

msgctxt "4220"
msgid "……いや。"
msgstr "……Disagreeable."

msgctxt "4231"
msgid ""
"ならいい。\n"
"あいつのことはあいつに任せておけ。"
msgstr "It's fine. Leave him to him."

msgctxt "4278"
msgid ""
"今は東洋様の死の裏を探ることだ。\n"
"それができる人間は俺たち以外にいない。"
msgstr ""
"Now it's time to find out behind the death of Toyo-sama. Only we can do "
"that."

msgctxt "4351"
msgid "吉田東洋を親とする俺たちだけなんだ。"
msgstr "We are the only ones whose parents are Yoshida Toyo."

msgctxt "4388"
msgid ""
"ああ、そうだな、俺にはやるべきことがある……\n"
"だから俺は武市半平太とは違う道を選んだ。"
msgstr ""
"Oh yeah, I have something to do ... So I chose a different path than Takechi"
" Hanpeita."

msgctxt "4476"
msgid "……死ぬなよ、兄弟。"
msgstr "...... Don't die, brothers."

msgctxt "4498"
msgid "（今日はもう休むか……）"
msgstr "(Do you want to take a rest today ...)"

msgctxt "4523"
msgid "（もう少し、街でもぶらつくか……）"
msgstr "(Do you hang out in the city a little more ...)"

msgctxt "4558"
msgid "（そろそろ寝るとしよう……）"
msgstr "(Let's go to bed soon ...)"

msgctxt "5360"
msgid "中岡"
msgstr "Nakaoka"

msgctxt "5413"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "5713"
msgid "休む"
msgstr "rest"

msgctxt "5718"
msgid "まだ休まない"
msgstr "I haven't rested yet"
